# Local agent / scratch state — EXCEPT the committed harness layer
# (.claude/{settings.json,rules,commands,agents}). Anything else under
# .claude/ (todos, local state, settings.local.json) stays local.
# NB: `.claude/*` not `.claude/` — git can't re-include below an ignored dir.
.claude/*
!.claude/settings.json
!.claude/rules/
!.claude/commands/
!.claude/agents/
!.claude/hooks/
.remember/
.superpowers/

# Netlify CLI auto-generated
deno.lock

# Playwright MCP scratch output (page snapshots, screenshots, downloads)
.playwright-mcp/

# Ephemeral smoke-test artifacts at repo ROOT only.
# Intentional images live in docs/images/ (a subdir — unaffected by these root-anchored globs).
/*.png
/*.csv

# SDD scratch (ledger, briefs, reports, review packages) — never commit
.superpowers/
